abstract: Manchester United beats Cambridge, 3-0, in FA Cup replay; other soccer news noted.
lead_paragraph: United overcame fourth-tier Cambridge in an F.A. Cup replay, winning by 3-0 less than two weeks after a humbling 0-0 draw.
